<taxonomicName box="[559,815,1324,1350]" class="Equisetopsida" family="Equisetaceae" genus="Equisetum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Equisetales" pageId="32" pageNumber="33" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sylvaticum">
<emphasis box="[559,815,1324,1350]" italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="33">Equisetum sylvaticum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Not ant-attended.
</paragraph>
